title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1994-10-01
description:
Set 1: Help On The Way > Slipknot > Franklin's Tower, Walkin' Blues, Althea, Me & My Uncle* > Big River*, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, So Many Roads, Promised Land

Set 2: Scarlet Begonias > Fire On The Mountain, Way to Go Home, Saint Of Circumstance > Terrapin Station > Drums > Space > The Last Time > Stella Blue > One More Saturday Night

E: Liberty

reviews.review_text: Solid Huge setlist and pretty well played.  One of the better shows of the year
